9, \"to\": 2391}, {\"ngram\": \"the Omnium\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her winning performances at Strade Bianche, Paris-Roubaix, and second overall at the Giro d'Italia Women indicate that she is at her best form for these Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6735895337452116e-15, \"text\": \"Strade Bianche\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Strade_Bianche\"}, {\"begin\": 2504, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"score\": 0.9816675037644488, \"rank\": 0.004431782209560121, \"text\": \"Paris-Roubaix\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\\u2013Roubaix\"}, {\"begin\": 2545, \"end\": 2558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d'Italia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.093329152010156e-18, \"text\": \"Giro d'Italia\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\", \"Q15091377\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d'Italia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Giro_d'Italia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her winning performances\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"her best form\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2602}, {\"ngram\": \"these Olympic Games\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And as a two-time Tour of Flanders champion, watch for Kopecky to set the tone for the women's road race in Paris.\", \"from\": 2628, \"to\": 2742, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2736, \"end\": 2741, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.65442159731475e-31, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedi